              </ul>
            </div>
          ) : skill.slug === 'the-principles-and-practice-workshops' ? (
            <div class="text-lg text-[color:var(--color-text-muted)] leading-relaxed text-left space-y-4">
              <p>
                <span aria-label="graduation cap" role="img">üéì</span> <strong>The Principles and Practice Workshops</strong><br/>
                Our Principles and Practice Workshops deliver immersive, hands-on training designed to empower researchers, students, and professionals in the fields of bioinformatics and artificial intelligence. Each session is crafted to bridge the gap between foundational theory and real-world application, ensuring participants gain both conceptual understanding and practical skills.
              </p>
              <ul class="list-none space-y-2">
                <li><span aria-label="clipboard" role="img">üìã</span> <strong>Research Strategy and Experimental Design:</strong> Receive expert guidance on designing robust research studies and experimental protocols. Learn how to formulate research questions, select appropriate methodologies, and ensure reproducibility in your work.</li>
                <li><span aria-label="bar chart" role="img">üìä</span> <strong>Bioinformatics and Analytics Support:</strong> Get comprehensive support for data analysis, statistical modeling, and computational methods. Our workshops cover essential tools and workflows for managing, analyzing, and visualizing complex biological data.</li>
                <li><span aria-label="robot" role="img">ü§ñ</span> <strong>Artificial Intelligence for Research and Health:</strong> Explore the latest AI and machine learning applications in biomedical research and healthcare. Gain hands-on experience with algorithms, data pipelines, and real-world case studies that demonstrate the transformative power of AI in science and medicine.</li>
              </ul>
