                <span aria-label="sparkles" role="img">‚ú®</span> <strong>Why Choose Our Workshops?</strong><br/>
                - Interactive, small-group sessions led by experienced instructors<br/>
                - Real-world datasets and practical exercises<br/>
                - Focus on both principles and hands-on practice<br/>
                - Support for all experience levels, from beginner to advanced
              </p>
              <p>
                Join us to build your expertise, expand your research toolkit, and connect with a vibrant community of learners and innovators.
              </p>
            </div>
          ) : skill.slug === 'research-strategy-and-experimental-design' ? (
            <div class="text-lg text-[color:var(--color-text-muted)] leading-relaxed text-left space-y-4">
              <p>
                <span aria-label="clipboard" role="img">üìã</span> <strong>Research Strategy and Experimental Design</strong><br/>
                Our Research Strategy and Experimental Design service provides expert guidance to help you plan, structure, and execute robust research projects. We work with you from the earliest stages‚Äîformulating research questions and hypotheses‚Äîthrough to the design of experiments and protocols that maximize rigor, reproducibility, and impact.
