                - Support for interdisciplinary and collaborative projects<br/>
                - Emphasis on ethical, transparent, and impactful science
              </p>
              <p>
                Let us help you turn your research ideas into successful, well-designed studies that stand up to peer review and drive scientific progress.
              </p>
            </div>
          ) : (
            <p class="text-lg text-[color:var(--color-text-muted)] leading-relaxed text-center">{skill.description}</p>
          )}
        </div>
      </section>
    </main>
    <Footer />
  </body>
</html>
